text: Carlock may refer to: ==People with the surname== *Dave Carlock, American record producer. *Keith Carlock, American jazz drummer. *Robert Carlock, American screenwriter and producer. ==Locations== *Carlock, Illinois, USA. *J. J. Carlock House, historic house in New Jersey, USA. *Carlock Building, historic building in Lubbock, Texas, USA. ==Fictional characters== Carlocks are the antagonists of the Regular Show episode, "Journey to the Bottom of the Crash Pit".
